				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$f_3$$\end{document}f3 in Fig. S5). Functions controlling these periods are given in Fig. S5.Figure 1
Age distribution function \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
